==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unargued
<hw>Un*ar"gued</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Not
argued or debated.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Not argued against; undisputed.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Milton.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>Not censured.</def> <mark>[A Latinism. Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>B. Jonson.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unarm</ent>⟦br⟧
